divs: Sighting DetailsI reviewed pictures of the Royal Wedding that I took from my television on April 29, 2011. Upon reviewing the photos I discovered two "very unusual" beings sitting on my landing watching me through a mirror that reflects into both rooms. Every person that I have showed this picture to says, "it looks like aliens." This has really bothered me and I would really like this picture to be examined by someone that can tell me what I am seeing in this photo. I have to say these "things" look like nothing I have ever seen nor want to see. I hope they are not here all the time and I don't know it for I never have taken pictures of anything on my TV before this day.
Summary: I caught a picture of two unknown weird alien-like "things" in my house sitting on my stair landing.
